title: United Kingdom Imports - Stone, Plaster, Cement, Mica & Similar Materials
description: Imports - Stone, Plaster, Cement, Mica & Similar Materials in the United Kingdom increased to 162 GBP Million in September from 161.86 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Stone, Plaster, Cement, Mica & Similar M in the United Kingdom averaged 85.13 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 177.81 GBP Million in June of 2022 and a record low of 32.71 GBP Million in January of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Stone, Plaster, Cement, Mica & Similar.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
